                  <li><b>Seasonal pricing</b> that reduces over spring and summer, then increases slightly over autumn and winter.</li>
                </ul>
                <%= partial "shared/sign_up_classic" %>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="small-12 medium-6 columns padding">
            <div class="white columns plan-container padding plan-space">
                <h2 class="medium-text-center grey-type">Powershop Lite</h2>
                <img alt="Fixed Plan" class="img-space" title="Fix and forget" src="/assets/images/resi/lite.png" />
                <p class="text-left">This is the option if you like a good deal but prefer a bit more simplicity, and donâ€™t mind missing out on the extra savings you can get from shopping.</p>
                <ul class="plan-option">
                  <li>No access to the shop or our specials, just a <b>simple monthly bill</b> to pay.</li>
